Kier to Deliver Projects in U.K. Valued Up to 1 Billion Pounds

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-09-15T07:07:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/kier-to-deliver-projects-in-u-k-valued-up-to-1-billion-pounds.html
Kier Group Plc (KIE)  said it has been
named as sole contractor to deliver a range of construction
projects throughout the U.K. on behalf of Scape.  The Scape National Minor Works framework will run for four
years and is valued between 750 million pounds and 1 billion
pounds.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Ermakova in London at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
